# checkbox-snap

This directory contains source code for all of the variants of checkbox-snap.
The variants being different snaps for different releases of Ubuntu.

`common_series_classic` directory contains files that are shared between all classic series.
`common_series_uc` directory contains files that are shared between all Ubuntu Core series.
 By default they are not present in the corresponding series subdirectories.

# Snapping

Before you launch snapcraft, run `./prepare_classic.sh` or `./prepare_uc.sh` with an argument signifying which version of the snap you're planning to build. E.g.
```
./prepare_classic.sh series_classic22.sh
```
or
```
./prepare_uc.sh series_uc22.sh
```

